            TypeError: cannot concatenate bounded integer sequence and None

        TESTS:

        The discussion at :issue:`15820` explains why the following are good tests::

            sage: BoundedIntegerSequence(21, [0,0]) + BoundedIntegerSequence(21, [0,0])
